'''Leo Geeris''' is a prominent [[Dutch people|Dutch]] [[businessman]] and [[investor]]. He was ranked in the 350 richest persons in the [[Netherlands]], and is especially active in the [[real estate]] sector. Leo Geeris is a sponsor for many charities and sport events.

