{{Infobox Magazine | title = Ziarul Financiar | image_file = | image_size = 200px | image_caption = | editor = Sorin Pislaru | editor_title = | frequency = | circulation = | category = [[Business Daily]] | company = | publisher = [[PubliMedia International]] | firstdate = | country = {{Flag|ROU}} | language = [[Romanian language|Romanian]] | website = [http://www.zf.ro/ www.zf.ro] | issn = 1454-2641 | oclc = 780376884 }} '''''Ziarul Financiar''''' is a daily financial [[newspaper]] published in [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]]. Aside from business information, it features sections focusing on careers and properties, as well as a special Sunday newspaper. ''Ziarul Financiar'' also publishes [[Transylvania]]n, [[Proprietati]], [[Ziarul de duminica]], [[Profesii]], [[Dupa afaceri]], supplements and a monthly magazine, ''[[go4it!]]'', which is provided freely to the newspaper's subscribers.
